{"tid":1568762,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[文宣請入] 形象工程係和理非既責任，唔係勇武既責任","createTime":"2019-09-14T11:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T01:40:55.000Z","uid":33904,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e56203f05aeb4301b8d2e60b1063f1c537981a43","tid":1568762,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:23:16.000Z","msg":"我地唔需要怕比人話勇武暴力打人唔合理，<br />\n唔好阻住勇武出手驚有損形象，令外國唔幫手。<br />\n<br />\n維持形象靠既係文宣：<br />\n721 白衫無差別<br />\n荃灣被斬致殘廢<br />\n連儂牆被斬到要用呼吸機<br />\n鴨脷洲鏹水<br />\n<br />\n大把彈藥比我地同外國講我地既行動只係保護自己，黑警選擇性執法，親中恐怖分子大部分冇受到法律制裁，我地需要以武制暴，阻止針對年輕人同示威者既暴力惡化。<br />\n<br />\n可以用以上四單野整英文文宣，<br />\ntitle 寫點解香港示威者要用武力還擊，<br />\n再放twitter。"},{"pid":"c95c5bc42b2b9632226f9c9e4d4f50558b8ce7c3","tid":1568762,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f6a277f9314371c3845af193434e992f1a2a2e","tid":1568762,"uid":33904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"暴力 = 出師無名用既武力<br />\n<br />\n出師有名既話，<br />\n核彈都唔會割，<br />\n當年美國出原子彈有冇話佢？<br />\n<br />\n武力升級，文宣配合解釋先會出師有名。"},{"pid":"c9d003a44de08408ae72f1bbee597e284b47e957","tid":1568762,"uid":191556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">915 （國際民主日）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />英領集會1200+銅鑼灣1430<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c6716e3a9185d099ee8